<div class="status-header">
    <div class="tag" style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #166534;">Security Confirmed</div>
    <h1>Escrow Payment Received</h1>
    <p>Funds for Order #{{orderId}} have been successfully secured in the BulkMandi Escrow account.</p>
</div>

<div class="highlight-box" style="background-color: #f0fdf4; border-color: #dcfce7;">
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label" style="color: #166534;">Transaction Status</div>
        <div class="info-value" style="font-size: 20px; color: #14532d;">₹{{amount}} Secured</div>
        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #15803d;">Verified by BulkMandi Payments</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="divider" style="background-color: #bbf7d0;"></div>
    
    <p style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; color: #14532d;">
        Seller Action: You are now authorized to dispatch the material.
    </p>
</div>

<p>
    The payment will be released to the seller as per the platform rules (80% on Dispatch, 20% on Delivery Acceptance).
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
    <a href="{{orderUrl}}" class="btn">View Order Details</a>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center;">
    This order is protected by BulkMandi Escrow, ensuring a safe and transparent transaction for both parties.
</p>
